---
// 丽芙定制光标 — 光环 + 核心 + 涟漪
// 设计：不替换原生光标，在其上方叠加主题色光环
---

<style is:global>
  #lifu-cursor-core {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; z-index: 99999;
    width: 8px; height: 8px; pointer-events: none;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(var(--lifu-cursor-accent, 212,168,83), 0.9);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(var(--lifu-cursor-accent, 212,168,83), 0.7),
                0 0 30px rgba(var(--lifu-cursor-accent, 212,168,83), 0.25);
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    will-change: transform;
    transition: background 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.45, 0, 0.55, 1),
                box-shadow 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.45, 0, 0.55, 1);
  }

  @keyframes ringRotate {
    from { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(0deg); }
    to { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(360deg); }
  }
  #lifu-cursor-ring {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; z-index: 99998;
    width: 32px; height: 32px; pointer-events: none;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1.2px solid rgba(var(--lifu-cursor-accent, 212,168,83), 0.35);
    box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(var(--lifu-cursor-accent, 212,168,83), 0.15),
                inset 0 0 18px rgba(var(--lifu-cursor-accent, 212,168,83), 0.06);
    animation: ringRotate 12s linear infinite;
    will-change: transform;
    transition: border-color 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.45, 0, 0.55, 1),
                box-shadow 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.45, 0, 0.55, 1);
  }

  @keyframes ringPulse {
    0%, 100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); opacity: 0.6; }
    50% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.15); opacity: 1; }
  }
  #lifu-cursor-pulse {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; z-index: 99997;
    width: 48px; height: 48px; pointer-events: none;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 0.8px solid rgba(var(--lifu-cursor-accent, 212,168,83), 0.18);
    animation: ringPulse 2.5s cubic-bezier(0.45, 0, 0.55, 1) infinite;
    will-change: transform;
    transition: border-color 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.45, 0, 0.55, 1);
  }

  /* 点击涟漪 */
  @keyframes clickRipple {
    0% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0.5); opacity: 0.8; }
    100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(2.5); opacity: 0; }
  }
  .lifu-cursor-ripple {
    position: fixed; z-index: 99996; pointer-events: none;
    width: 24px; height: 24px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--lifu-cursor-accent, 212,168,83), 0.5);
    animation: clickRipple 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.22, 0.61, 0.36, 1) forwards;
  }

  :root { --lifu-cursor-accent: 212, 168, 83; }
  .dark { --lifu-cursor-accent: 126, 174, 228; }

  @media (hover: none), (pointer: coarse) {
    #lifu-cursor-core, #lifu-cursor-ring, #lifu-cursor-pulse { display: none !important; }
  }
</style>

<div aria-hidden="true">
  <div id="lifu-cursor-core"></div>
  <div id="lifu-cursor-ring"></div>
  <div id="lifu-cursor-pulse"></div>
</div>

<script is:inline>
  (function() {
    if (window.matchMedia('(pointer: coarse)').matches || window.matchMedia('(hover: none)').matches) return;

    var core, ring, pulse;
    var mouseX = -100, mouseY = -100, curX = -100, curY = -100, raf = 0;
    var now, then = 0, elapsed, fpsInterval = 1000 / 120;
    var lastMove = 0, idle = false;

    function findElements() {
      core = core || document.getElementById('lifu-cursor-core');
      ring = ring || document.getElementById('lifu-cursor-ring');
      pulse = pulse || document.getElementById('lifu-cursor-pulse');
    }
    findElements();
    if (!core) return;

    function onMove(e) { mouseX = e.clientX; mouseY = e.clientY; lastMove = Date.now(); idle = false; }

    function onClick(e) {
      var r = document.createElement('div');
      r.className = 'lifu-cursor-ripple';
      r.style.left = e.clientX + 'px';
      r.style.top = e.clientY + 'px';
      document.body.appendChild(r);
      setTimeout(function() { r.remove(); }, 600);
    }

    function loop(timestamp) {
      now = timestamp;
      elapsed = now - then;

      if (elapsed > fpsInterval) {
        then = now - (elapsed % fpsInterval);

        var dx = mouseX - curX;
        var dy = mouseY - curY;

        if (Date.now() - lastMove > 300 && !idle) { idle = true; }
        if (Date.now() - lastMove < 300) { idle = false; }

        var speed = idle ? 0.04 : 0.1;
        curX += dx * speed;
        curY += dy * speed;

        findElements();
        var cx = Math.round(curX), cy = Math.round(curY);

        if (core) core.style.transform = 'translate3d(' + cx + 'px, ' + cy + 'px, 0)';
        if (ring) ring.style.transform = 'translate3d(' + cx + 'px, ' + cy + 'px, 0) rotate(0deg)';
        if (pulse) pulse.style.transform = 'translate3d(' + cx + 'px, ' + cy + 'px, 0) scale(1)';
      }

      raf = requestAnimationFrame(loop);
    }

    document.addEventListener('mousemove', onMove, { passive: true });
    document.addEventListener('click', onClick, { passive: true });
    then = performance.now();
    raf = requestAnimationFrame(loop);
  })();
</script>
